GEMS INFO
=========================================================

tzinfo
  required for timezone support

redcloth
  greencloth derives from redcloth

rmagick
  used to scale avatars and build thumbnails

open4
  used by latex renderer (optional)

SyslogLogger
  improved logging (optional)

hpricot
  used by the plugin webrat
